const clientID = `${process.env.clientID}` // your clientID
const clientSecret = `${process.env.clientSecret}` // your client Secret
const redirect_uri = encodeURIComponent(`${process.env.redirect_uri}`) // your domain

export {clientID, clientSecret, redirect_uri}
